          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "多蒙老丈渡江河，"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "千金谢礼不为多。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员下。伍员上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "再与老丈把话说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军为何去而复返？"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是我去而复转，倘若后面追兵到来，莫说我打此经过，休要走漏我的消息。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住。我好心倒变了坏意，这便怎么处？待我投江一死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，那旁有人来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在那里。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（渔父投江下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伍员 （扑灯蛾） 老丈投江河，老丈投江河，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为我投江死，美名万古波，美名万古波。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，我不免将绳索砍断，断却行人，我就是这个主意。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员砍绳，下。）"
        }
      ],
